Release LTS.421.5 of August 1, 2024
New features
1.
The new "synchronizeDomainUsers" function allows integrating the system with Microsoft Active Directory. It enables the option to synchronize data and domain users from an external provider.
2.
Virtual column registry set up was improved, possibility to add attributes from different object types was added.
Changes and improvements
"Object chat" widget
was improved;
Adding existing attribute was improved, system remembers previously selected object types;
Setting up
tab
’s name and color by algorithm was stabilized;
Running expressions when creating child objects was optimized;
Viewing algorithm’s service information is now available in "Read" mode;
Creating and viewing new objects for
permissions control of authorization object
type in
folder registry
was stabilized;
Accessing object registry from created object type copy was stabilized;
Opening
multiple choice object attribute
by clicking on value was improved;
Selecting attribute values in registry editing mode was stabilized;
Previewing and downloading files in completed task of business process was optimized and display of buttons in control panel of incoming and outgoing documents was improved;
Search filter’s reset values button’s functionality is now applied to search bar;
Returning to previous page was stabilized;
Edoc improvements: downloading and adding document to print in Review mod was stabilized, creating print form using algorithm, tagging users in comments, scrolling and working with document in multiple windows were improved;
Operation of algorithms, authorization/registration page loading time and system notifications were improved;
"Algorithm. Random aggregation for a form cell" and "Algorithm. Aggregation by reporting form indicators" object visuals were improved.
Registry column editing option was stabilized;
Business process search bar was improved;
updateProviderUserData function was stabilized;
Display of outgoing documents configured on stage was stabilized.
